text: Cologna is a Swiss civil parish of Poschiavo, Graubünden Cologna may also refer to: *Cologna (Pellezzano), an Italian civil parish of Pellezzano, Campania *Cologna (Tirano), an Italian civil parish of Tirano, Lombardy *Cologna Veneta, a municipality in the Province of Verona in the Italian region Veneto ==People with the surname== *Dario Cologna (born 1986), Swiss skier, brother of Gianluca *Gianluca Cologna (born 1990), Swiss skier, brother of Dario ==See also== *Cologno (disambiguation) *Cologne (disambiguation)
